title: DDFP 403: Week 10 Preview & Déjà Vu
itunes:title: DDFP 403: Week 10 Preview & Déjà Vu
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank and Matt "Money" Smith to make their Week 10 "Red Challenge Flag" picks. The guys then discus "Déjà Vu" moments from past match ups, that could come into play this week. Lastly, Shek meets up with David Koechner for another addition of "Daves of our lives". All this and more on DDFP.
